{
	"name": "Nightly Profit Mod",
	"author": "CDGameDev",
	"description": "THIS MOD IS TESTED AND WORKING FOR BETA 25.1. If you run into any issues on another version, comment below and I'll get it sorted out;ALWAYS USE THE LATEST VERSION!\n\nAre you tired of using a calculator to figure out how much money your company is making/losing from its services? Want a way to easily find it out? Now you can with the Nightly Profit Mod.\n\nThis mod creates a new page, showcasing how much money you are making Nightly. (The mod only calculates how much you make from income on services, how much you spend on servers, staff wages and corporate benefits. It doesn't take into account things like buying furniture or paying one off staff fees when they start working for you).\n\nThe mod displays the profit in a new format; GRAPHS, making the old TABLE view obsolete (and thus this has been removed), but I'm sure you won't miss that mess of a display method. You can also choose how many days of data you want to show, with the options being: 3 Days/5 Days/1 Week/2 Weeks/1 Month /2 Months/1 Year.\n\nIf you have any problems with the mod, or want to make a suggestion, please contact me (iTzHayleyUK) on the Devhives' discord server: https://discord.gg/devhives"
}
